				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>For the record, I chose theocide over deicide in the drafting process because &quot;theo&quot; is more widely recognizable as referring to gods whereas &quot;dei&quot; is more ambiguous.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-180659-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup> And it kinda sounds better in my opinion.</p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-180659-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. Based on my own observations, at least.</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
