pan class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1588688804" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1588688804" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drhawkwind" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=993076&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1588688804" alt="DrHawkwind" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=993076)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drhawkwind" >DrHawkwind</a></span> for crit over chat.</p> <hr /> <p>So, bit of an experiment here. It's the third in a four-part series (click <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/slipping-away">here</a> and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-eschaton">here</a> for the first two) and a spiritual successor to <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4755">SCP-4755</a>. A proper hub for this stuff will be up eventually.</p> <p>Glad to see it's sticking right now, had a fair amount of trepidation. I hope you enjoyed!</p> 
